    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shape having a flattened curve between convex sections of similar flattened curves, particularly in reference to furniture pieces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
